7.15<br />\n川普簽署《香港自治法案》取消香港特殊待遇<br />\n<br />\n基於中國於2020年6月30日通過《港版國安法》後，確定香港（香港）特別行政區不再具有足夠的自治權。因此，川普表示，「香港已<span class=\"red\">不再</span>是香港了，<span class=\"red\">不能再</span>和自由市場競爭」。川普強調，<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">香港將獲得與大陸相同待遇，無特權、也無特殊經濟地位</span></strong></span>，亦<span class=\"red\">不允許</span>從美國出口敏感技術到香港或從香港再出口，包括<span class=\"red\">取消</span>香港獨立關稅區。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2021.04.06<br />\n廢林肯：「會延續去年的決定，繼續<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong><span class=\"red\">暫停</span></strong></span>給予香港特殊待遇，包括「獨立關稅區」地位。」<br />\n弊燈on9粉：正呀喂！廢林好撚硬  <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"843544359f04684b2a40be9afbf99e718e7beeb7","tid":2477693,"uid":297997,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T14:51:19.000Z","msg":"仲查<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢條仆街"},{"pid":"41d555b57a124993d1c3a191ae36d07af237e3e5","tid":2477693,"uid":332119,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T14:52:14.000Z","msg":"連登仔有興趣可以了解下03年美國點樣開伊拉克波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95a07c990c73b350ddad455b7d4e72d92db23079","tid":2477693,"uid":294518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"41d555b57a124993d1c3a191ae36d07af237e3e5","tid":2477693,"uid":332119,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T14:52:14.000Z","msg":"連登仔有興趣可以了解下03年美國點樣開伊拉克波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-06T14:55:33.000Z","msg":"唔比查就<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br /